      "translated": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "translated": "It's so good."
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "translated": "And next is Airi Momoi."
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "translated": "Here is the trained version."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "translated": "This outfit is similar to the one Honoka was wearing earlier,"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "translated": "but the skirt part is slightly different. Airi has flowers spread out like a pannier,"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "translated": "and it's just so cute."
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "translated": "I can't stop looking at it."
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "translated": "The droplets scattered around her make it look like the rain just stopped."
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "translated": "That feeling really reminds me of the story."
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "translated": "And here is the untrained art."
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "translated": "This was in the story too, but Airi really is"
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "translated": "always worried about Shizuku Hinomori."
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "translated": "She's always asking,"
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "translated": "\"Are you okay?\""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "translated": "Since Shizuku tends to keep things to herself,"
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "translated": "..."
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "translated": "Airi is always there to check on her."
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "translated": "Seriously."
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "translated": "Without Airi, the Shizuku we know today wouldn't exist."
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "translated": "Even back in the theater days, Airi encouraged her so much during her time in Q-T,"
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "translated": "so you can really see the bond between these two."
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "translated": "And then we have Haruka Kiritani."
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "translated": "The untrained art."
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "translated": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "translated": "Look at this little frog getting startled."
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "translated": "Isn't this expression just the cutest?"
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "translated": "She's landing right on a leaf."
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "translated": "It's great."
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "translated": "Haruka's outfit has a bit of orange mixed with the red, which is also super cute."
    }
  ]
